com.yahoo.bullet.aggregations

Class Distribution

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.yahoo.bullet.aggregations.SketchingStrategy<QuantileSketch>
      • com.yahoo.bullet.aggregations.Distribution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Strategy, Closable, Initializable, Monoidal

    public class Distribution
extends SketchingStrategy<QuantileSketch>
    This Strategy uses QuantileSketch to find distributions of a numeric field. Based on the size configured for the sketch, the normalized rank error can be determined and tightly bound.
